So we're gonna start really simple, alright?

00:00:43.510 --> 00:00:48.829
And the basic step goes like, basically, you
hop on the right, and you push, and you hop

00:00:48.829 --> 00:00:49.989
again on your right.

00:00:49.989 --> 00:00:53.149
So you hop, push, hop, push, okay?

