00:00:57.820 --> 00:00:59.080
Hopping on your right, pushing.

00:00:59.080 --> 00:01:01.950
Now, the arms, we're gonna coordinate the
arms, okay?

00:01:01.950 --> 00:01:06.560
Just so we look clean, 'cause everything is
always about just looking clean.

00:01:06.560 --> 00:01:08.079
Presentation, alright?

00:01:08.079 --> 00:01:13.549
So the arms is, we're going out position So
we're going here, push....here, push, here,

00:01:13.549 --> 00:01:15.380
push, here, push here.

00:01:15.380 --> 00:01:19.229
Push, here, push, here, push, here, push,
here.

00:01:19.229 --> 00:01:21.649
Push, here, push, here, push...alright?

00:01:21.649 --> 00:01:23.960
So that's the basic step, alright?

00:01:23.960 --> 00:01:26.799
Now, we're gonna try that with some music,
